edu.stanford.math.plex4.kd

Class KDEuclideanMetricSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.math.plex4.metric.impl.ObjectSearchableFiniteMetricSpace<double[]>
      • edu.stanford.math.plex4.kd.KDEuclideanMetricSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractIntMetricSpace, AbstractObjectMetric<double[]>, AbstractObjectMetricSpace<double[]>, AbstractSearchableMetricSpace<double[]>

    public class KDEuclideanMetricSpace
extends ObjectSearchableFiniteMetricSpace<double[]>
    This class implements the AbstractSearchableMetricSpace interface for providing query functions for a Euclidean metric space. The underlying search operations are performed with the help of a KD-tree.
    Author:
    Andrew Tausz
